<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٣٢٠٤ - حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/644">إِسْمَاعِيلَ </a>قَالَ حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5235">قَيْسٌ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4435">أَبِي مَسْعُودٍ </a><span class="special">﵁</span> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«الشَّمْسُ وَالْقَمَرُ لَا يَنْكَسِفَانِ لِمَوْتِ أَحَدٍ وَلَا لِحَيَاتِهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٠٩⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلَكِنَّهُمَا آيَتَانِ مِنْ آيَاتِ اللهِ فَإِذَا رَأَيْتُمُوهُمَا فَصَلُّوا.»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>